import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Member } from '../entity/member'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register', templateUrl: './register.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register.component.css'], }) export class RegisterComponent { showForgetPasswordContent = false; memberData: Member = { email: '', password: '', forgetPasswordAnswer: '', memberId: 0, firstName: '', lastName: '', mobileNo: '', }; onSubmit() { console.log(this.memberData); } showForgetPassword() { this.showForgetPasswordContent = true; } }
